txt.en: You have defeated Bosnauk and the roving trolls that followed him, earning the gratitude of the people of the Westfold.
Warband: Bosnauk and the Roving Trolls
Roving trolls terrorize the Westfold, led by the mighty Bosnauk.
Bosnauk and his roving band of trolls can be found in the centre of the Westfold.\n\nYou should defeat Bosnauk.
